# --- YieldForge Web — client configuration (12-factor) ---------------------------
# Copy to `.env.local` for local dev. NEVER commit real values, and NEVER put secrets
# here: anything the browser needs must be prefixed NEXT_PUBLIC_ and is public.

# Backend API origin the Next.js server proxies to. D1 (PLAN-200): the browser calls the
# app's OWN origin (e.g. /api/...) and Next.js rewrites to this target, so the SPEC-003
# HttpOnly session cookie stays same-origin (no CORS, no SameSite=None). Server-side only —
# not exposed to the browser. Wired into next.config in the auth phase (SPEC-200 Phase 4).
API_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:8080
